 &nbsp;<a href="http://www.wrathofdragonclaw.org/cgi-bin/ultimatebb.cgi?ubb=private_message&u=00000109"><img src="http://www.wrathofdragonclaw.org/NonCGI/priv_message.gif" border='0' alt="Send New Private Message"></a>&nbsp;
 &nbsp; &nbsp;
<a href="http://www.wrathofdragonclaw.org/cgi-bin/ultimatebb.cgi?ubb=edit_post&f=17&t=000018&reply_num=000000&u=00000109"><img src="http://www.wrathofdragonclaw.org/NonCGI/edit_ubb6.gif" border="0" alt="Edit/Delete Post"></a>
 &nbsp;<a href="http://www.wrathofdragonclaw.org/cgi-bin/ultimatebb.cgi?ubb=reply&f=17&t=000018&replyto=000000"><img src="http://www.wrathofdragonclaw.org/NonCGI/quote_ubb6.gif" border="0" alt="Reply With Quote"></a>&nbsp;
