( Though my piss poor English and grammar, how can this story go without ME???Muhahahah Sorry to ruin this story with my comic ways  <IMG SRC="http://www.wrathofdragonclaw.org/NonCGI/biggrin.gif"> )<P>Meanwhile, back at the Emerald Tiger Den, a foul stench took over the smell of sweet ale. "WTF is that smell? " demanded Gomb. Suddenly the doors burst open with a bang.<P>A grumpy looking darkelf and never before seen maiden walked in. Trailing them, FAR behind them... was another darkelf. It was the source of the aweful smell. All eyes grazed on the grumpy one as the all silently grabbed hold of thier trustful sidearm. <P>The Grumpy one stared at the tenseful standoff and said " BAH!! ". Suddenly a white FLASH, blinding everyone in the room, and standing before everyone was a HUGE Barbarian. All gazed and sighed relief. It was Raichu. At the sight of Raichu, all knew that the other two that came in with them was Keeki and Tome ( /bonk everyone for not knowing that smell ).<P>It has been a long time since anyone from the guild seen these three. For the past 6 months, Raichu have been wandering the Planes of Hate while Keeki and Tome been tucked away in Skyfire.<P>"The POS Ranger finally arrives " declared Gomb. Raichu smiled. Raichu knew to be on best behavior, with Gomb here,the beautiful Amethyst must be near. <P>"Are we late? Where is McDuffy? " said Keeki. "They left right before Amethyst and I got here, and were told to head off towards them once we get a more to join our party" declared Gomb. As Tome opened his mouth to utter his first words, " We'll Join .." ,a voice near the fireplace behind Gomb said with a giggle " Before you JOIN, DUDE go wash up!!!!!" With that, Keeki led Tome to the back while Raichu sat next to his old friend Gomb.<P>When they returned, Gomb and Raichu got up, put away the maps and got up. Lets go! Mcduffy will need much help.<P><p><FONT COLOR="#3299CC" SIZE="1" FACE="Verdana, Arial">[Edited 1 time by Raichu Babai on 21 April 2001 at 13: