 | <a href="javascript:ce_enforce('17','000018','000038');">Problem??</a>
  </FONT>
<HR size="1" color="#3299CC">
<FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">
Great just great, i have the perfect spell for this situation but no, I didn't bother to learn it. Well sometimes its best to look out for one's own survival. <P>Quickly memorizing abscond and several other small teleports, Vandril stands up and pours his mana into it. With a soft pop, he vanishes.<P>Reappearing at what is spposed to be the safest spot nearby, I laugh once again at how usless that spell is. Not more than 10 feet from me is that dragon, working its own magic, which with no doubt will summon each one of us individually for it to slaughter at our leisure. <P>Well I am never one to die with mana at my disposal. Crying at the top of my lungs hoping that I will be heard in true wizard fashion, I scream. And launch into magic that will hopefully interupt its first round of summons.
<br>
<br>
<br>
