 | <a href="javascript:ce_enforce('17','000018','000039');">Problem??</a>
  </FONT>
<HR size="1" color="#3299CC">
<FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">
For the first time in many years the dragon was at a loss for what to do.<P>It's bind spot was only about 1000 yards from where the fight had begun, but it was far enough away that it knew it could get several heals off then summon the party there individualy to kill them. Now this impudent mortal arrives, screaming its fool head off! What to do...kill him or heal...<P>In the end, pride overwhelmed the dragon. It would kill this foolish one for daring to face it! Yes, his bones crunching beneath its mighty talons would indeed be satisfying!<P>The dragon turned to the wizard and launched a viscious series of claw and bite attacks...this one's pain would become legendary!
<br>
<br>
